        <p>
          Shadow Computers is the trading name for Steve Roberts, a UK-based Senior Software Engineer
          with over 25 years' experience building and maintaining production systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          Steve's primary work focuses on full-stack development, backend systems, APIs, and
          cloud-based environments. Shadow Computers is a personal, part-time project that allows him
          to support families and small businesses while remaining hands-on with real-world technology.
        </p>
        <p>
          This ensures that Steve's development work remains closely connected to practical,
          real-world usage — working with actual users, hardware, operating systems, hosting
          environments, and media production scenarios rather than purely abstract engineering.
        </p>
        <p>
          For more information on Steve Roberts' full career history and experience, please visit his
          personal website: <a href="https://steveroberts.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">steveroberts.me <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>.
        </p>
        
        <div class="notice-box notice-box--info">
